n unparalleled opportunity to travel in time, back to the excitement of ancient Olympia.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aGreece -- Civilization -- To 146 B.C. 0aGreece -- Social life and customs -- To 146 B.C. 0aOlympia (Greece : Ancient sanctuary). 0aOlympic games (Ancient). 0aOlympics. 7aHISTORY / Ancient / Greece.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030016029140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300160291423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300160291/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles